---
/** Scroll-linked manifesto. site.js splits [data-split] lines into staggered words. */
---
<section id="manifesto" data-screen-label="Manifesto">
  <div class="inner">
    <span class="kicker">// Manifesto</span>
    <p class="mline" data-split>We don't chase trends<span class="accent-amber">.</span></p>
    <p class="mline" data-split>We build brands that <span class="em-cyan">outlast</span> them because growth is <span class="em-amber">engineered</span>.</p>
    <p class="mline" data-split>We see the system, not just the symptom<span class="accent-amber">.</span></p>
    <p class="mline mscript"><span class="script">Design is only the beginning.</span></p>
  </div>
</section>
